---
title: Arroz Con Pollo with Smoky Lime Crema
description: Inspired by the traditional Latin American chicken and rice dish, arroz con pollo, our version deploys a bold Mexican Spice Blend to add flavor to quickly cooked chicken, stirred into richly fragrant and fluffy rice. For even more flavor, the chicken is sizzled with caramelized onions and earthy, piquant peppers. But we don't stop there—how about a drizzle of smoky, rich and bright lime crema? Right?! We thought so!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/arroz-con-pollo-f0cf8652.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipecards/card/arroz-con-pollo-6304f0489cb593d9ff05dcdc-b1e368b8.pdf
course: main course
time required: 1 hour
cuisine: Mexican
servings: 2
author: HelloFresh
source: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipes/arroz-con-pollo-6304f0489cb593d9ff05dcdc
